==病因==
[[File:Agenesia_de_vagina2.png|right]] 

基因{{le|WNT4|WNT4}}已经清楚地解释了这种体征的典型版本。基因变异导致[[亮氨酸|亮氨酸]]取代了此前位于12位[[氨基酸|氨基酸]]的[[脯氨酸|脯氨酸]]残基<ref name="EIGHT" />。它锐减了核级量的{{le|β蛋白|β catenin}}。此外，它消除了类固醇合成酶3β-11-羟基类固醇脱氢酶（{{lang|en|3β-hydroxysteriod dehydrogenase}}）和17α羟化酶（{{lang|en|17α-hydroxylase}}）的抑制。因此，在缺乏WNT4基因蛋白，苗勒管只能呈现变形或者消失。女性的生殖器官，如[[宫颈|宫颈]]、[[输卵管|输卵管]]、[[卵巢|卵巢]]和阴道组织，均受此影响<ref>{{cite web|title=WNT4 Müllerian aplasia and ovarian dysfunction|url=http://ghr.nlm.nih.gov/condition/wnt4-mullerian-aplasia-and-ovarian-dysfunction|accessdate=2012-08-18|publisher=Genetics Home Reference}}</ref>。

一项报道称此疾患与[[17号染色体|17号染色体]]（17q12）的缺失突变有关。{{le|LHX1|LHX1}}基因位于该区域，并可能是此类并增的原因之一<ref name="Ledig2012">{{Cite journal|title=Frame shift mutation of LHX1 is associated with Mayer-Rokitansky-Kuster-Hauser (MRKH) syndrome|url=https://academic.oup.com/humrep/article-lookup/doi/10.1093/humrep/des206|last=Ledig|first=S.|last2=Brucker|first2=S.|date=2012-09-01|journal=Human Reproduction|issue=9|doi=10.1093/humrep/des206|volume=27|pages=2872–2875|language=en|issn=0268-1161|last3=Barresi|first3=G.|last4=Schomburg|first4=J.|last5=Rall|first5=K.|last6=Wieacker|first6=P.}}</ref>。

==患病率==
患病率预估为每12000名女性XX染色体中有一例变异症状<ref name="Pittock">{{Cite journal|title=Mayer-Rokitansky-Küster-Hauser anomaly and its associated malformations|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/ajmg.a.30721|last=Pittock|first=Siobhán T.|last2=Babovic-Vuksanovic|first2=Dusica|date=2005-06-15|journal=American Journal of Medical Genetics Part A|issue=3|doi=10.1002/ajmg.a.30721|volume=135A|pages=314–316|language=en|issn=1552-4825|pmid=15887261|last3=Lteif|first3=Aida}}</ref>。 [[歐登堡的阿瑪莉埃|希腊王后阿玛利亚]]在去世后被发现有此症状，她未能给丈夫[[奥托一世_(希腊)|奥托一世]]增添子嗣，导致政权被推翻<ref name="LossOfThrone">{{Cite journal|title=The lack of a child, the loss of a throne: the infertility of the first royal couple of Greece (1833–62)|url=http://www.rcpe.ac.uk/journal/issue/journal_41_1/poulakou-rebelakou.pdf|last=Poulakou-Rebelakou|first=E|last2=Tsiamis|first2=C|date=2011-03-01|journal=Journal of the Royal College of Physicians of Edinburgh|issue=1|doi=10.4997/JRCPE.2011.115|volume=41|pages=73–77|pmid=21365071|last3=Tompros|first3=N|last4=Creatsas|first4=G}}</ref>。

==治疗==

人造一个功能性阴道已经被多种治疗方法所证实，然而对于子宫缺乏的情况，手术仍然无法实现怀孕。标准的方法是通过使用阴道扩张器和/或手术移植人造阴道，实现插入式性交。在麦恩道氏过程（麦恩道氏再造阴道之整型术）中<ref>{{cite journal|title=McIndoe Vaginoplasty: Revisited|author=S. Saraf|url=http://www.ispub.com/journal/the_internet_journal_of_gynecology_and_obstetrics/volume_6_number_2_6/article/mcindoe_vaginoplasty_revisited.html|journal=The Internet Journal of Gynecology and Obstetrics|publisher=Internet Scientific Publications|accessdate=2009-07-17|issue=2|year=2007|volume=6|issn=1528-8439|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090327141337/http://www.ispub.com/journal/the_internet_journal_of_gynecology_and_obstetrics/volume_6_number_2_6/article/mcindoe_vaginoplasty_revisited.html|archivedate=2009-03-27|deadurl=yes|author2=P. Saraf}}</ref>，皮肤移植被运用于[[阴道成形术|人工阴道]]成型。在手术后，仍要防止阴道{{le|狭窄|stenosis}}。[[维奇耶堤氏阴道成形术|维奇耶堤氏阴道成形术]]已经实现病人可以具备正常功能的阴道<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Creation of an artificial vagina in Rokitansky-Küster-Hauser syndrome|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/5319813|last=Vecchietti|first=G.|date=1965-03|journal=Attualita Di Ostetricia E Ginecologia|issue=2|volume=11|pages=131–147|issn=0004-7317|pmid=5319813}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=A new laparoscopic procedure for creation of a neovagina in Mayer-Rokitansky-Kuster-Hauser syndrome|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8893702|last=Fedele|first=L.|last2=Bianchi|first2=S.|date=1996-11|journal=Fertility and Sterility|issue=5|doi=10.1016/s0015-0282(16)58653-1|volume=66|pages=854–857|issn=0015-0282|pmid=8893702|last3=Tozzi|first3=L.|last4=Borruto|first4=F.|last5=Vignali|first5=M.}}</ref>。在维奇耶堤氏手术过程中，通过腹腔镜手术进入腹部和肚脐，安置一个称为“橄榄树”的小型塑膠装置，呈螺纹状对应阴道区域，并以螺旋状嵌入阴道皮肤。这些螺纹连接一个牵引装置。手术时间约45分钟，牵引装置保持日常牵引，使得“橄榄拉”能够向内延伸阴道约1厘米/天，创造了一个约7厘米深度的阴道<ref>{{cite web|title=Vecchietti Procedure|url=http://www.uclh.nhs.uk/NR/rdonlyres/07C53DB9-6C67-4375-86B4-DB9DF42635AD/21989/VecchiettiProcedure.pdf|accessdate=2010-04-03|publisher=University College University Hospitals|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090411233240/http://www.uclh.nhs.uk/NR/rdonlyres/07C53DB9-6C67-4375-86B4-DB9DF42635AD/21989/VecchiettiProcedure.pdf|archivedate=2009-04-11|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。另一种方法，是通过结肠腹腔镜手术，结合{{le|自体干细胞移植|autotransplant}}技术，切除一个[[乙状结肠|乙状结肠]]；报告称其可以被移植为一个良好的功能性阴道<ref>{{cite journal|title=Modernes Management der angeborenen (Mayer-Rokitansky- Küster-Hauser, MRKH-Syndrom) und erworbenen Vaginalaplasie|author=Hold MK|url=http://www.frauenheilkunde-aktuell.ch/frauenheilkunde-d/PDF-Ordner-FHA-Frauenheilkunde-aktuell/Frauenheilkunde-Aktuell-Ausgabe-01-07/FHA-Arikel04_12_Modernes_Management_der_Vaginalaplasie.pdf|date=2007-01-16|journal=Frauenheilkunde-Aktuell|language=de}}</ref>。

在一些苗勒管发育不全病例中，{{le|子宫移植|Uterine transplant}}也被采用，但是手术仍然处于试验阶段<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Preliminary results of the first human uterus transplantation from a multiorgan donor|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23084266|last=Ozkan|first=Omer|last2=Akar|first2=Munire Erman|date=2013-02|journal=Fertility and Sterility|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.fertnstert.2012.09.035|volume=99|pages=470–476|issn=1556-5653|pmid=23084266|last3=Ozkan|first3=Ozlenen|last4=Erdogan|first4=Okan|last5=Hadimioglu|first5=Necmiye|last6=Yilmaz|first6=Murat|last7=Gunseren|first7=Filiz|last8=Cincik|first8=Mehmet|last9=Pestereli|first9=Elif}}</ref>。因为[[卵巢|卵巢]]存在，患者可以通过[[体外受精|体外受精]]以及{{le|胚胎移植|embryo transfer}}到一个[[妊娠载体|妊娠载体]]。一些患者会选择领养<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Evaluation and management of cases of primary amenorrhoea with MRKH syndrome|url=https://www.banglajol.info/index.php/BMJK/article/view/13626|last=Akhter|first=Nasreen|last2=Begum|first2=Badrunnesa|date=2013-02-03|journal=Bangladesh Medical Journal Khulna|issue=1-2|doi=10.3329/bmjk.v45i1-2.13626|volume=45|pages=24–29|issn=2311-8016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Rokitansky Syndrome: Information for Parents / Carers|url=http://www.cmft.nhs.uk/media/455258/11%20131%20rokitansky%20syndrome.pdf|accessdate=11 April 2014|publisher=St Mary's Hospital, Manchester|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219191141/http://www.cmft.nhs.uk/media/455258/11%20131%20rokitansky%20syndrome.pdf|archive-date=2017-02-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在2014年10月，一位36岁的瑞典妇女成为移植子宫并成功生育健康孩子的首位患者。她天生没有子宫，但有正常功能的卵巢。她和孩子父亲通过体外受精，产生11个胚胎，然后冷冻。[[哥德堡大学|哥德堡大学]]的医生通过子宫移植，供体是一个61岁的朋友。在移植一年后，这些冷冻胚胎中的一个开始发育。在31周母亲出现子痫前期症状后，小男孩早产出身。

前沿研究有一些实验室培育结构，其不受非阴道组织的并发症影响，仍然通过人体自身的细胞作为源语资源<ref>{{cite web|title=Laboratory-grown vaginas implanted in patients|url=http://www.kurzweilai.net/laboratory-grown-vaginas-implanted-in-patients|accessdate=14 April 2014}}</ref><ref name="#1">{{Cite journal|title=Tissue-engineered autologous vaginal organs in patients: a pilot cohort study|url=https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(14)60542-0/abstract|last=Raya-Rivera|first=Atlántida M.|last2=Esquiliano|first2=Diego|date=2014-07-26|journal=The Lancet|issue=9940|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(14)60542-0|volume=384|pages=329–336|language=En|issn=0140-6736|pmid=24726478|last3=Fierro-Pastrana|first3=Reyna|last4=López-Bayghen|first4=Esther|last5=Valencia|first5=Pedro|last6=Ordorica-Flores|first6=Ricardo|last7=Soker|first7=Shay|last8=Yoo|first8=James J.|last9=Atala|first9=Anthony}}</ref>。最近的工程型阴道技术可以使用患者自身细胞，生产出完成结构的功能性阴道，实现月经和性高潮<ref>{{Cite web|title=Engineered vaginas grown in women for the first time|url=https://www.newscientist.com/article/dn25399-engineered-vaginas-grown-in-women-for-the-first-time/?ignored=irrelevant|access-date=2022-04-05|work=New Scientist|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name="#1"/>。

